text: E. palustris may refer to: * Eimeria palustris, an apicomplexan parasite species that infects the marsh rice rat * Eleocharis palustris, the common spike-rush, creeping spike-rush or marsh spike-rush, a plant species growing in wetlands throughout the Boreal Kingdom * Epipactis palustris, the marsh helleborine, an orchid species ==See also== * Palustris (disambiguation)
title: E. palustris
